{"tid":1393113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參與過塞鐵行動，不合作運動最重要就係民意！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:43:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:33:50.000Z","uid":129622,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d3062e690af77face9cefa53bf2bea170ccb6d","tid":1393113,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"最近搞好多罷工罷課 都係主動參與<br />\n但塞巴塞鐵係會影響到好大部份非主動參與市民<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔反對塞交通 公民抗命少不免整個社會都要付出代價</span><br />\n但和理非式公民抗命係需要好大既民意去支持<br />\n所以一直話燒生果套行唔通 因為佢需要八 九成市民先推翻到暴政<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁唔代表唔可以做 只係我地唔可以做得太多太密 令市民覺得煩厭</span><br />\n唔係講緊議題上「民意逆轉」 而係行動方針上「民意逆轉」 <br />\n<br />\n同其他行動唔同塞鐵行動既人比較集中 易交流<br />\n希望大家真係決定塞鐵 請有禮貌向<strong>任何</strong> 係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>任何受影響既有禮貌地市民解釋</strong></span><br />\n佢鬧我地阻住返工 就幫佢搵其他交通離開<br />\n佢鬧我地唔讀好書 就同佢講用埋年假抗爭<br />\n<br />\n現場見到唔少兄弟同人嘈到面紅耳赤 面對藍絲廢中廢老係好激氣 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從來抗爭既路都難行 但我地可以用唔同方式去應對 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"306b0da580e0834d7f91fbe83f3779d54cc13901","tid":1393113,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37431bfc7643857d27cf60cc3f22883e400dcc05","tid":1393113,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"e163ba1889fa0523a0b48dcdbed38fddf1914563","tid":1393113,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"其實點解塞鐵行動會咁大爭議？<br />\n因為規模未夠大<br />\n每次都只係塞一條線  其他地區打工仔心諗點解唔過黎幫我罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthat's why 要一次全面性塞過海線+3隧既大規模行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如何合法癱瘓港鐵</span><br />\n一人一喼港鐵fashion show大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390849</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"96fd7b3e7921a95d1b9ceb5880e8496cb0a1956e","tid":1393113,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e163ba1889fa0523a0b48dcdbed38fddf1914563","tid":1393113,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"其實點解塞鐵行動會咁大爭議？<br />\n因為規模未夠大<br />\n每次都只係塞一條線  其他地區打工仔心諗點解唔過黎幫我罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthat's why 要一次全面性塞過海線+3隧既大規模行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如何合法癱瘓港鐵</span><br />\n一人一喼港鐵fashion show大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390849</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"好多人唔係淨係返工<br />\n我都支持罷鐵 但真係唔可以搞得密 同埋要同其他市民解釋"},{"pid":"bd5c42b9eb14a2d24eb2bf8056b9e020eb4b2f86","tid":1393113,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364963ea0678081cafb5af3d5e682aab61e47a1b","tid":1393113,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"e42244e344cc9bf8c8cfe2ee96983944eb08c9bf","tid":1393113,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71590b64b82c4e388e2b6b1ac2a1e62c2691860","tid":1393113